HEADWORD: Twire-pipe
<hw>Twire"-pipe`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A vagabond
musician.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>You are an ass, a <qex>twire-pipe</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Beau. &
